{"text_id":28986,"tokens":["In"," this"," study",","," we"," present"," a"," spectrophoto","metric"," model"," that"," has"," been"," applied"," to"," the"," Wide","-","Field"," Infrared"," Survey"," Explorer"," (","W","INGS",")"," dataset"," of"," cluster"," galaxies","."," The"," motivation"," for"," this"," research"," was"," to"," investigate"," the"," physical"," properties"," that"," govern"," the"," evolution"," of"," galaxies"," in"," clusters",","," including"," their"," star"," formation"," histories",","," chemical"," enrichment",","," and"," mass"," assembly","."," By"," analyzing"," the"," spectroscopic"," data"," from"," the"," W","INGS"," survey",","," we"," aimed"," to"," identify"," key"," correlations"," between"," these"," properties"," and"," determine"," their"," underlying"," physical"," drivers",".","\n\n","Our"," model"," is"," based"," on"," a"," Bayesian"," approach",","," which"," allows"," us"," to"," quantify"," the"," uncertainties"," associated"," with"," our"," results"," and"," provides"," a"," robust"," statistical"," framework"," for"," comparing"," different"," models","."," Using"," this"," method",","," we"," found"," that"," the"," star"," formation"," histories"," of"," galaxies"," in"," clusters"," are"," complex"," and"," exhibit"," a"," wide"," range"," of"," times","cales"," and"," amplitudes"," of"," star"," formation"," activity","."," We"," also"," observed"," that"," the"," chemical"," enrichment"," histories"," of"," these"," galaxies"," are"," strongly"," influenced"," by"," their"," stellar"," masses",","," with"," more"," massive"," galaxies"," showing"," higher"," metal","licity",".","\n\n","Overall",","," our"," results"," support"," the"," hypothesis"," that"," the"," evolution"," of"," galaxies"," in"," clusters"," is"," driven"," by"," a"," combination"," of"," internal"," processes",","," such"," as"," star"," formation"," and"," chemical"," enrichment",","," as"," well"," as"," external"," processes",","," such"," as"," tidal"," interactions"," and"," gas"," stripping","."," Our"," spectrophoto","metric"," model"," provides"," a"," powerful"," tool"," for"," understanding"," these"," complex"," mechanisms"," and"," sheds"," new"," light"," on"," the"," fundamental"," processes"," that"," shape"," the"," evolution"," of"," galaxies"," in"," the"," universe","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo","label":1}